node.title: Man arrested in South Canterbury over Palmerston North shooting
node.description: A man has been arrested in Twizel, South Canterbury this morning in relation to a shooting in Palmerston North early this month.
node.content:
["A man has been arrested in Twizel, South Canterbury this morning in relation to a shooting in Palmerston North early this month.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "The shooting happened in Highbury on 2 November.", "The 28-year-old Manawat\u016b man has been charged with wounding with intent to cause grievous bodily harm.", "He will appear in Timaru District Court on Monday.", "Police are still seeking another man in relation to the incident."]
